feedback_text: Love the product overall. Would be great to have a dark mode option for late night work sessions.
Your customer support team is absolutely fantastic. Sarah helped me resolve my integration issue in under an hour.
Dashboard keeps crashing when I try to export reports. Very frustrating. Happening for 3 days now.
Would love to see Slack integration. We use Slack for everything and manual copy-paste is tedious.
The new analytics dashboard is exactly what we needed. Great job on the recent update!
Product is good but pricing feels steep for small businesses. Consider a startup tier?
Bulk upload feature would save us hours. Currently adding items one by one.
Critical: Data sync has been failing for our team. We've lost work. Need immediate attention.
Switched from a competitor last month. Your UX is so much cleaner. No regrets!
Getting started was confusing. More video tutorials would help new users.
Calendar view for projects would be helpful. Currently using a separate tool for scheduling.
Your API documentation is the best I've seen. Integration was smooth.
Pages load slowly when we have more than 100 items. Optimization needed.
Would like to see SOC2 compliance badge. Our security team is asking.
The mobile app update is fantastic! Finally can check things on the go.
Love the product but had to downgrade due to budget. Miss the Pro features.
Team permissions could be more granular. Need view-only access for some users.
Best customer success team. Monthly check-ins actually provide value.
Export to PDF formatting is broken. Images overlap with text.
CRM integration would be a game changer for our workflow.
Affordable and effective. Perfect for organizations with limited budgets.
Training resources are outdated. UI has changed but docs haven't.
Inventory management module would make this a complete solution for us.
Recommended to 3 other companies already. Keep up the great work!
Search function is slow with large datasets. Please optimize.
Custom fields would help us track property-specific data.
Audit trail feature saved us during compliance review. Thank you!
Notifications not working reliably. Sometimes delayed by hours.
Great value for the Basic tier. Considering upgrade to Pro next quarter.
ROI has been incredible. Paid for itself in the first month.
